graph TB
    subgraph "ModelMesh Serving Component"
        Controller[modelmesh-controller<br/>Deployment]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>Service]
        Controller -->|validates CRs| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Runtime Pods (per ServingRuntime)"
        ModelMesh[ModelMesh Container<br/>8080/TCP gRPC]
        RESTProxy[REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP]
        Puller[Storage Helper/Puller<br/>8086/TCP gRPC]
        RuntimeAdapter[Runtime Adapter<br/>8085/TCP gRPC]
        ModelServer[Model Server<br/>8001/TCP gRPC]

        RESTProxy -->|translates to gRPC| ModelMesh
        ModelMesh -->|routes inference| RuntimeAdapter
        RuntimeAdapter -->|communicates| ModelServer
        Puller -->|loads models| ModelServer
    end

    subgraph "Storage & State"
        etcd[(etcd StatefulSet<br/>2379/TCP)]
        S3[(S3/Minio Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS)]
    end

    User[User/Client] -->|creates| PredictorCR[Predictor CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
    User -->|creates| ServingRuntimeCR[ServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
    User -->|creates optional| InferenceServiceCR[InferenceService CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1]

    PredictorCR -->|watched by| Controller
    ServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| Controller
    InferenceServiceCR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates| RuntimeDeployment[Runtime Deployment]
    Controller -->|creates| Service[modelmesh-serving Service<br/>8033/TCP gRPC]
    Controller -->|manages state| etcd

    RuntimeDeployment -->|contains| ModelMesh
    RuntimeDeployment -->|contains| RESTProxy
    RuntimeDeployment -->|contains| Puller
    RuntimeDeployment -->|contains| RuntimeAdapter
    RuntimeDeployment -->|contains| ModelServer

    ModelMesh -->|state coordination| etcd
    Puller -->|retrieves models| S3

    Client[Inference Client] -->|gRPC or HTTP| Service
    Service -->|routes to| ModelMesh

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ModelMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RESTProxy fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Puller fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RuntimeAdapter fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ModelServer fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style etcd fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style S3 fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PredictorCR fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style ServingRuntimeCR fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style InferenceServiceCR fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
